# Testing Standards

## Backend

- Use xUnit.
- Use FluentAssertions.

## Integration Tests

- Test endpoints end-to-end.
- Use test containers when possible.

## Architecture Tests

Validate:
- No feature coupling
- Proper dependency direction
- CQRS separation

## Frontend

- Use Vitest.
- Use React Testing Library.

## Naming

MethodName_State_ExpectedBehavior